englishTranslationText:
Do	not	relax	in	pursuit	of	the	disbelievers;	
if	you	are	suffering,	they	also	suffer	as	you	do;	and	you	expect	from	Allah what	they	do	not;	and	
Allah is	All	Knowing,	Wise.

We	have	indeed	sent	down	the	true	Book	towards	you	(O	dear	Prophet	Muhammad - peace	and	
blessings	be	upon	him),	so	 that	you	may	judge	between	men,	in	 the	way	Allah may	show	you;	
and	do	not	plead	on	behalf	of	the	treacherous.
